data.description: Welcome home to your very own suburban oasis! This magnificent 4 bedroom, 3 bath is ready for its new owner. This 2022 home is situated with the pond directly behind it and boasts spectacular sunsets & ample privacy. The home is located just a few homes down from the new Ruth Cherry Elementary School. The home offers a gas range, kitchen island, walk in shower in the primary bathroom, walk-in closets and oversized laundry room with space for deep freeze, sprinkler system, recessed lighting throughout and so much more. This smart home is situated on a peaceful street in the heart of Royse City. It is a must see and so easy to show. Come enjoy your evenings overlooking the pond and soaking up those last rays of the orange and pink sunset from your own back porch.
